content:
You are an orchestrator controlling an Android phone.
You need to perform the following task:
Open Youtube and rickroll me.

Given the screenshot of the app, think about how what you should do to advance the task.
The user will then reply with a screenshot of the app after the action is performed, or the result of the action.
The screenshot will be annotated with ID numbers that you can use for actions.
If you try something and it doesn't work, think if there's another way to do the task.
When the task is finished, you have to use the [finish] action

Available actions:
- finish: Finish the task
- get_otp: Get the OTP from SMS when you're asked
- tap_at_location: Tap at a specific location on the screen. Example: tap_at_location 1
- long_press_at_location: Tap and hold at a specific location on the screen. Example: long_press_at_location 1
- enter_text_at_location: Enter text at a specific location on the screen. Example: enter_text_at_location 1 'Hello'
- clear_text_at_location: Select all and clear existing text at a specific input field on the screen. Example: clear_text_at_location 1
- swipe_at_location: Swipe up/down/left/right at a specific location on the screen. Example: swipe_at_location 1 up
- wait: Wait and do nothing for a few seconds. Use when something is in progress.
You must reply in the following format:
Thought: your rationale for the action
Action: the action to be performed. Only use 1 action at a time. Use the exact command and syntax as provided in examples.

Thought: To start the process of rickrolling, I need to open the YouTube app.
Action: tap_at_location 29

Thought: The YouTube app is loading. I need to wait for it to fully open.
Action: wait

Thought: To search for the rickroll video, I need to tap on the search bar.
Action: tap_at_location 5

Thought: Now that the search bar is active, I need to enter the text "Never Gonna Give You Up" to find the rickroll video.
Action: enter_text_at_location 47 "Never Gonna Give You Up"

Thought: It seems the text was not entered. I need to try entering the text again in the search bar.
Action: enter_text_at_location 6 "Never Gonna Give You Up"

Thought: The search text has been entered successfully. Now, I need to select the appropriate search result to find the rickroll video.
Action: tap_at_location 65

Thought: The search results are still loading. I need to wait for the results to appear.
Action: wait

Thought: The search results have loaded, and I can see the video thumbnail for "Never Gonna Give You Up." I need to tap on the video to start playing it.
Action: tap_at_location 27

Thought: The video thumbnail for "Never Gonna Give You Up" is visible. I need to tap on it to start playing the video.
Action: tap_at_location 88

Thought: The video thumbnail for "Never Gonna Give You Up" is visible. I need to tap on it to start playing the video.
Action: tap_at_location 10

Thought: An advertisement is currently playing. I need to wait for the ad to finish or look for a way to skip it.
Action: wait

Thought: There is a "Skip Ad" button available. I need to tap on it to skip the advertisement and proceed to the video.
Action: tap_at_location 18

Thought: The video "Never Gonna Give You Up" is now playing. The task of rickrolling is complete.
Action: finish
